Package com.siqi.taskadmin.menu

Enum CommandWord

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<CommandWord>
      • com.siqi.taskadmin.menu.CommandWord

  • public enum CommandWord
extends java.lang.Enum<CommandWord>
    This class is part of the "ToDoly" application. "ToDoly" is a small application which is used to administrate all the tasks owned by user. This class holds an enumeration of all command word known to the application. It is used to recognise commands when they are typed in.
    Version:
    2018.10.04
    Author:
    Siqi Qian
